All Implemented Interfaces:
PruningStrategy
public class LexicalDiversityPruningStrategy
extends DiversityPruningStrategy

A diversity pruning strategy that defines signs to be notCompellinglyDifferent if the set of open class stems is the same. The POS classes of interest are set in the constructor.
